channel.title: Everything is working but my server won't work
channel.description: I made a silabsoft server and it just won't work! My port is open 43594. My firewall is off. I-P is set to mine and when I hit runserver it says it's running but i don't get anything on silabsoft. Also, when I run compiler it says Note:stream.java overrides a deprecated API. Note: recompile with -xlint:deprecation for details. Press any key to continue. Is it supposed to do that and PLEASE HELP FIX MY SERVER. I CAN DO TEAMVIEWER IF YOU LIKE!!!
